parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the SRS system can prevent the airbag from deploying in the event of an accident, potentially leading to serious injury or fatality.
symptoms: The SRS light stays on or blinks
indicating a malfunction in the system
and the airbag may not deploy in the event of an accident.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Engine Oil Gasket Failure (Manifold Oil Gasket Breakage)
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the engine oil gasket can cause the oil to heat up, leading to a potential engine fire, which can result in serious accidents or injuries.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Engine Stalling or Dying While Accelerating
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The engine stalling or dying while accelerating can cause loss of vehicle control, leading to accidents or near-miss situations.
symptoms: Engine dying or stalling when increasing speed

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ignition switch can cause the key to come out of the ignition without the transmission being in park, which can lead to unintended vehicle movement, accidents, and damage to property.
symptoms: The key comes out of the ignition without the transmission being in park
the vehicle rolls or moves unexpectedly
the vehicle is not in park when the key is removed.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission shift interlock can cause the transmission to not engage into park, leading to unintended vehicle movement, accidents, and damage to property.
symptoms: The transmission does not engage into park
the vehicle rolls or moves unexpectedly
the vehicle is not in park when the key is removed.
